            <article id="aboutUsImg">
                <div class="overlay">
                    <h4 class="aboutUsInfo"><em>Who's Vanilla Story</em></h4>
                    <p class="aboutUsParagraph"><small>Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting
                            industry.</small></p>
                    <div class="col text-center">
                        <a href="#"><button type="button" class="btn btn-warning text-white">More
